Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.49,0:00:21.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lying in a strong heart is the power of deduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.29,0:00:22.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stepping into the truth with a sharp rhythm!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:25.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What lies under the hat will now be revealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:26.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure's incredible past!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:28.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.38,0:00:30.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:32.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.45,0:01:45.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While accompanying Sonoko on her shopping\Nspree, we came to this department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.29,0:01:53.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then, Uncle got involved in\NInspector Megure's sting operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:01:58.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Inspector Was investigating a series\Nof cases involving bludgeoned women.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.18,0:02:04.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, in the department store's underground\Nparking garage, Ran discovered a woman's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:19.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure continued his investigation,\Nbut he didn't appear to be his usual self...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:22.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Superintendent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:25.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, allow us to investigate just a little longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:26.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we're getting somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:30.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I have a feeling that the culprit\Nis still around here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.50,0:02:34.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you must.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:37.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Megure...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.59,0:02:43.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that you're still thinking\Nback to that case from before?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.89,0:02:49.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About what it is you hide away under your hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:58.90,Title,,0,0,0,,Megure's Sealed Secret\N(Part Two)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:16.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:17.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could I borrow your keys?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:23.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This case seems like it's gonna take a while, so I'd\Nlike to put my stuff in the car and visit the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:25.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, don't be too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:27.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The store will be closing soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:29.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:30.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you take mine too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:31.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:39.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:40.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:43.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, look at how this other car is parked!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:45.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a strange way to park!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:48.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't even open the passenger side door like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:56.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:02.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, I just heard back from her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:04.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.13,0:04:08.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As we thought, she was in her car\Nbefore going to the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:10.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:13.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I still don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.23,0:04:16.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why is he only after fashionable\Nyoung girls who drive cars?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.44,0:04:19.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or is there some other connection?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:22.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something that we overlooked connecting those four...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:25.45,Signs,,0,0,0,,{Sign}Restroom Closed\NFor Cleaning\N\NPlease accept our\Napologies for the\Ninconvenience.\N\NHaido{Signature}\NDepartment Store
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:25.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:27.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:32.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't they wait to clean until after they've closed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:34.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The next restroom is up on the 8th floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:38.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have such bad luck with these restrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:42.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for visiting our department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:44.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll be closing soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:46.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please come again soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:47.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:48.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:50.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll take the body now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:01.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, her leg slipped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:02.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:06.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:08.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The shoe doesn't fit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:11.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:15.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Earlier, you said there was\Nsomething wrong with that lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:16.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:20.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:24.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it's part of the ganguro fashion,\Nthey shouldn't have been missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:25.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:28.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could the culprit be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:30.72,Signs,,0,0,0,,{Sign}Restroom
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:40.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, don't turn the lights off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:41.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm still here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:45.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:47.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is anyone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:53.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:55.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Platform boots?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:06:02.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're saying that Aizawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who was killed in this\Nparking garage, was actually wearing platform boots?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.54,0:06:08.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeahâit's part of the ganguro fashion, so\Nthey wouldn't wear low-heeled pumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:10.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:12.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:18.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why would the criminal change the victim's shoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:20.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't want anyone to figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:26.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That he only goes after women\Nwho drive with platform boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:27.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:36.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, the other three victims\Nfollowed the ganguro fashion as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:42.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, those three must\Nhave had platform boots too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:42.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:46.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of platform boots...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:50.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The primary reason that Aizawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Ncaused that car accident a year ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:54.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was due to the fact she was\Ndriving with platform boots on...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:57.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which caused her braking to take longer than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:58.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what I heard from Yumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:00.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.64,0:07:01.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:07.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The deceased boy's mother and her ex-husband\Nargued that that was the cause of the accident, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:09.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The judge overruled them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:10.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ex-husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:12.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:15.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They divorced after the husband became an alcoholic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:19.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think that man's name was...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:21.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sadakane, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:24.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, right, that was his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:26.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:30.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't the guard's name... Sadakane?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:33.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, then, could that mean the culprit is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:35.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The security guard?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:42.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi, go get information on\Nthat accident from a year ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:42.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:45.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rest of you, go find the guard, Sadakane!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.73,0:07:46.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:50.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, how did you know all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:51.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't too difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:58.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit only attacked women who drove\Nwhile wearing platform boots, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:08:01.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From outside the car, the culprit can't see\Nwhat kind of shoes they're wearing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:04.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we know that the victims\Nshop at this department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:09.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As such, the only way the culprit would know\Nis to see them getting in and out of their cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:11.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why it had to be the guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:19.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, the victims said the\Nculprit was about 150 cm tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:23.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear the guard say he was 167 cm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:26.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're just playing stupid, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.11,0:08:32.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The girls only said that the culprit\Nwas the same height as them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:37.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At those times, they were wearing\Nplatform boots over 10 cm thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:40.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What that really meant was that the\Nculprit must've been 10 cm taller.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:42.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you already know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:45.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:48.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We measured their heights at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:53.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since they were coming for a police interview,\Nthey wouldn't wear informal platform boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:57.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, if he wanted to kill Aizawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.99,0:09:02.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do it in this parking complex rather\Nthan just go straight to her house?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:03.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten, Mouri?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:07.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim was 20 years old, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:11.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A year ago when she caused the\Naccident, she was considered a minor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:14.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Minors cannot have their addresses be\Nmade public according to the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:24.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of that, he waited at this department store\Nwhere his son died, hoping she'd return one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:33.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When she didn't appear, he broke down and began\Nattacking any woman who drove in platform boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:41.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, we got the backstory!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:46.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As we thought, the guard is the father of the\Nboy who died in the accident one year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:47.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.71,0:09:49.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is he at the moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:54.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that... his car is still in the\Nparking garage, but he's missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:10:00.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:02.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko hasn't come back yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:06.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She said she was just going to put her things\Nin the car and then going to the restroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:08.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Putting her stuff in the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:11.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, the shoes Sonoko's wearing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:19.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:20.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:21.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh, right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:23.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm still in the department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.93,0:10:25.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait until you hear what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:27.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:31.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right as I got out of the restroom,\Nthey turned the lights off...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:50.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:51.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something wrong, Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:52.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:53.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:56.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just thought I heard something weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:26.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She saw me... She saw me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.28,0:11:28.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She saw my face...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:30.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:31.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:33.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:37.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit saw Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r} doing\Nsomething in the car with the keys in hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:40.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He mistook her for a driver with platform boots!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:42.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:45.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is she right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:46.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inside the department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.22,0:11:48.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is the line cut?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:51.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's still connected, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:54.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can only hear a machine's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:55.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A machine's voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:11:58.90,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Please choose your background picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:01.65,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Press the button when your pose is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:04.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's a print club machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:07.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the department store, do they\Nhave a print club machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.28,0:12:08.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:13.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's two on the 10th floor, next\Nto the stairs for the restaurant...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:14.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.21,0:12:18.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The stores are closed, but\Nthe restaurants are still open.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:21.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} was headed up there to use\Nthe elevator to make her way back down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:22.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:24.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi, get the lights in the building back on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:27.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Megure and Satou, take the elevator\Nand search from top to bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:32.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The others, take the stairs and search bottom to top\Nin order to secure this girl and seize the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:32.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:35.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:36.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.81,0:12:41.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man, the Inspector seems fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:43.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.40,0:12:48.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This case has reminded him of the\Nfirst case he was involved in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:54.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, where's your daughter\Nand the boy with glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:34.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.54,0:13:37.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:39.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Sonoko's cell phone, no mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:43.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the customers in the restaurants\Nhaven't seen them...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.88,0:13:46.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} must've run into the department stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.63,0:13:49.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Takagi, where're the lights?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:55.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You girls are demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:57.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.31,0:14:03.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You disguise yourselves as cute girls in order to\Ncommit crimesâyou're nothing but little demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.73,0:14:06.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Demons have no right to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:12.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A blackout?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:13.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.45,0:14:14.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.33,0:14:19.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.33,0:14:21.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:23.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:25.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:31.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sounds like a number of things\Nare falling simultaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:32.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:33.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rice?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.64,0:14:35.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, something bigger...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.43,0:14:38.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be those little stones you put in a fish tank?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:40.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The pet shop is on the 4th floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:42.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That must mean she's on the 4th floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:43.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go check.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:54.28,Signs,,0,0,0,,{SignF10}Restaurant Floor\N{F9}Books & Beauty, Photos, Denistry\N{F8}Food, Housewares, CDs, Stationary\N{F7}Children's Apparel, Clocks, Glasses, Toys\N{F6}Misses & Plus Size Women's Apparel
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:05.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:09.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only intended to teach you a little lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:14.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you just had to go and see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:17.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:23.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:25.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:28.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's weird, there's no one in the pet shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:29.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:31.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.40,0:15:33.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing's broken and there's nothing on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:35.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:36.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That sound from before...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:40.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just had to see my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:15:57.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:04.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.31,0:16:05.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Feel good?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.94,0:16:06.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:13.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I asked if hurting others feels good to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:22.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You may think you're punishing evil\Nand being a bringer of justice, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:26.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is just a high school girl who\Nwanted to put things in a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:34.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You did this not for the sake of seeking\Njustice nor for avenging your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.63,0:16:36.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You did it solely out of rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:44.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For you it was just a conceited, meaningless\Ndiversion that trifled with people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:47.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you get it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:17:02.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just wanted that woman to apologize...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:07.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For her to wear proper shoes and\Napologize to my son in heaven...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:10.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all I wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:15.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That really was true in the beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:17.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:30.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.48,0:17:32.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:34.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:36.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:37.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.03,0:17:39.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:43.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, how did you know they were here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:44.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:48.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was led here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:50.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By these Go stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:54.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:17:56.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:59.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just my old wound reopening.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:03.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An old wound from the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:39.49,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Midoridai Police Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:38.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He got that wound from a previous case?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:40.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:45.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Megure hides the scar by wearing that hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.03,0:19:51.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But for a police officer, a scar is like a badge of honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:53.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He should be proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:55.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was more than twenty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:20:00.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, it was back when Megure\Nwas still a rookie on the force.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:04.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You may have heard about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:07.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The case where someone was\Nrunning over high-school girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:09.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.14,0:20:16.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit had been bullied by an all-girls gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.06,0:20:21.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was running them down in his car at\Nnight, when there was no one around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:26.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He targeted female delinquents\Nwho wore long, tight skirts...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.82,0:20:31.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ones they'd converted from their\Nschool uniforms to be their style.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:37.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At first, he only made light contact with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:41.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then it escalated and resulted in a fatality.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:51.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We warned all students not to wear that style of\Nskirt, so the case was settled for a while, until...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.14,0:20:57.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A high school girl showed up\Nwanting to be used as a decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.81,0:21:01.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wanted to find her friend's killer at any cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.73,0:21:07.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course we tried to stop her, but it seemed\Nshe despised the police, so she insisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:13.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With no other choice, I assigned\NMegure to keep an eye on her, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:31.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit tried to run over and kill\Nboth Megure and the girl with his car.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.14,0:21:39.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Luckily, Megure remembered the car number, so the\Nsuspect was caught very quicklyâbut at a high price.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.52,0:21:47.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Megure only hit his head, but the girl's\Nentire body was gravely injured...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:51.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the time we arrived, she was covered\Nin blood, and barely breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.04,0:21:58.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the reason why the Inspector\Nhas always kept his hat on...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.33,0:22:01.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.00,0:22:05.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He doesn't want others to ask him about the scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.92,0:22:10.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's always been reminded of that horrible case.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.30,0:22:15.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why Megure wears that\Nhatâto seal away that scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.23,0:22:18.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The scar that symbolizes that tragic memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.23,0:22:25.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's why the Inspector was against using decoys.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.03,0:22:28.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't want anyone else to die like that girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.53,0:22:30.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.91,0:22:33.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only said that she was gravely injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.49,0:22:34.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not that she died!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.54,0:22:38.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In fact, she's Megure'sâ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.41,0:22:40.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Superintendent Matsumoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.42,0:22:44.46,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It's an honor to have you come all the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.92,0:22:49.09,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Megure Midori\NMegure's Wife{CharCard}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.46,0:22:49.09,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Shiratori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} just left a few moments ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.51,0:22:52.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, they came by as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.55,0:22:55.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they all took a breather from work.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:22:59.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A scar on her forehead?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.81,0:23:01.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.02,0:23:02.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Midori!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.73,0:23:04.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you peel this apple for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.07,0:23:09.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, he enjoys being spoiled, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.53,0:23:13.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like I'll have to toughen him up\Nso he can return to the force soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.24,0:23:16.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, if you would, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.58,0:23:24.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, the Inspector said his wife,\NMidori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, was a delinquent in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.92,0:23:28.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that the real reason he wears that hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.92,0:23:33.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is because he doesn't want others to\Nmake fun of how he and his wife met?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.10,0:23:39.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heeey, not done yet?
